headline.print_headline: Kyrgios Announces Himself as Australian Standard Bearer
headline.main: Kyrgios Announces Himself as Australian Standard Bearer

lead_paragraph: The support was familiar but the face was not as teenager Nick Kyrgios ushered in a new era for Australian tennis on the lush grass of Wimbledon with an epic five-set triumph against 13th seed Richard Gasquet.
